content:
Absolutely—what would you like help with?

A few ways I can help:
- Explain a concept or summarize an article
- Write or edit emails, essays, resumes, or posts
- Debug or write code
- Plan projects, study schedules, workouts, or trips
- Brainstorm ideas (business, content, gifts)
- Do math or data analysis
- Practice interview questions or language skills
- Troubleshoot tech issues

If you can, tell me:
- Your goal and any deadline
- What you’ve tried so far
- Any constraints (tools, budget, word count, tone)
- Examples or files/snippets to reference
- Preferred output format (bullets, steps, code, etc.)

What should we tackle first?
